debate gorbachev proposed they return tuesday to vote on the 
strike ban and an overwhelming majority agreed tass said 
the package of government proposals also calls for imposing a 
special form of administration on railroads in armenia and 
azerbaijan with the ministries of railroads defense and interior 
responsible for protecting the railroads and their workers 
armenian activists say azerbaijani railroad workers recently 
have blocked the trains that armenia depends upon for 80 percent of 
