<TEXT>
like a roller coaster stuck on go 
the 60mph zodiac raft assaults mile after mile of 12foot swells 
startling puffins into diving for safety as tourists pursue an 
elusive minke whale 
blow 2 oclock yells a passenger pointing into a 
sunwashed horizon as the curved black back of the minke appears 
