ruling in an illinois case that federal workplace regulations dont 
bar state prosecutions 
five officials of chicago magnet wire corp await trial on 
charges of recklessly injuring 42 workers by exposing them to toxic 
chemicals extreme heat and other unsafe conditions at a 
wirecoating plant 
